##	INTRODUCTION

@node Introduction "Introduction"


Doroty  is a program to calculate isostatic frames, with features like
save/open ..  See the Directory Examples

Why is it called Doroty ? (That's not Dorothy, but DOROTY !) 

First:   I  (Max)  like  girls A LOT !  (Maybe too much...) expecially
beautiful  girls...  

So  I  dedicated  this program to this very special girl, and I'm sure
she  would  have loved it a lot !  (I'm a liar, she doesn't care about
structural program, she only liked to play Lotus !) :-C

Furthermore, everybody knows that a female program name is always more
interesting  than  a  so  called  TRX-MS767  or XCVZCGFADS or so on...
(HAW!  HAW!  HAW!)

Greetz 
        Max from AUTOMAX SOFTWARE


@endnode



