##
##	LIMITS
##

@node Limits "Limits"



Limits

Note  :   Max  Number  of  joints is 50.  The number of poles can't be
greater  than  95,  and  All Frame has an isostatic comportament so it
yelds only an isostatic answer.

The  Error Debug Mode is not very good, (I didn't have time...) but if
my  program  will get a good response from Internet I'll make a better
version.

By  the  way,  if  any  software  house  is  interested  in developing
structural  software,  please call AUTOMAX SOFTWARE !!!  Money is food
to my brain !!

@endnode


